      h2 Beijing, Tsinghua University, 17th - 19th September 2015.

      p The 2st Helsinki-HKUST-Tsinghua workshop on mobile big data and networking is a three-day workshop jointly organized by the University of Helsinki, Hong Kong University of Science and Technology, and Tsinghua University.
      p The workshop is intended to bring together professors, researchers and students to share ideas, experience and implementations related to cloud and mobile computing, including SDN, augmented reality (AR), urban computing, big data analysis, mobile offloading and 5G networks.

